                          [Root]
                            |
      ---------------------------------------------------
      |                        |                        |
   [A subtree]            [B subtree]               [C subtree]
       |                       |                        |
  ----------              --------------            -------------
  |   |   |               |     |     |             |      |     |
 [A1][A2][A3]          [B1]   [B2]  [B3]           [C1]   [C2]   [C3]
       |                      |                      |
    ------                -----------              ------------
    |    |                |    |    |              |     |    |
  [A21] [A22]           [B21][B22][B23]          [C21] [C22] [C23]


ðŸ§  What happens behind the scenes:

    Root forks tasks A, B, C
       * Worker 1 steals A subtree
       * Worker 2 steals B subtree
       * Worker 3 steals C subtree
       * As any worker finishes early â†’ it steals remaining children from others
       * processing ends when all leaves have joined upward